    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/60185ac884ea39a93f72288f7cf69f51.avif?t=1760520678\" width=577 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我，尼古拉斯·奥斯本，一个独立游戏开发业余爱好者，制作了这款Metroidvania游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/374591ee3a4c8f40affe94db27b97683.poster.avif?t=1760520678\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/374591ee3a4c8f40affe94db27b97683.webm?t=1760520678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/374591ee3a4c8f40affe94db27b97683.mp4?t=1760520678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你扮演年轻的太阳战士科林，但你只是个实习生。你握有一把神奇的太阳之矛，可以投掷、召回和用作平台！你所在的小镇被邪恶的蚊子手下毁灭，他们是昔日被困在月亮中的古老邪神库莱克斯的随从。为了阻止再次发生这样的事情，你决定找出它们的来历......你进入了一个被诅咒的土地，这只存在于书中的古老地下城市仍由一个产生几乎无尽蒸汽的强大热种子供电......曾经辉煌的SolLuna王国在此统治，但随着时间推移，信仰分歧引发了全面的内战。科林必须在一只小灵猫的引导下为自己寻找解决办法，战胜一切困难！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/a4e6dd5d3a28cf4c9aec54a71e168b49.poster.avif?t=1760520678\" width=600 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/a4e6dd5d3a28cf4c9aec54a71e168b49.webm?t=1760520678\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/a4e6dd5d3a28cf4c9aec54a71e168b49.mp4?t=1760520678\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2248230/extras/641c6a78a33f955c4bc1ac70de643892.avif?t=1760520678\" width=577 height=66 /></span></p>",
